    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that just sounds like a coping mechanism though. like people just say that so they don't have to face the reality that we're just biological accidents. if there is no objective purpose, then the \"beauty\" you're talking about is just a chemical trick in our brains to keep us moving. isn't it more honest to just admit that the struggle itself is irrational?",
